1144
01:00:41,438 --> 01:00:44,256


1145
01:00:44,256 --> 01:00:45,411
- Lad os gå.

1146
01:00:45,411 --> 01:00:49,127


1147
01:00:49,127 --> 01:00:50,891
- Det er Henry. Det er tyren.

